Package org.dice_research.squirrel.queue

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BlockingQueue<T>
    This extension of the UriQueue interface defines additional methods enabling the queue to manage the retrieving of chunks of URIs based on a defined key which is used to group the URIs.
    IpAddressBasedQueue Deprecated
    Use the more general BlockingQueue<InetAddress> interface instead.
    UriQueue
    Interface of a URI queue managing the URIs that should be crawled next.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDomainBasedQueue
    This abstract class manages two important aspects of an DomainBasedQueue.
    AbstractGroupingQueue<T>
    This abstract class manages two important aspects of a queue.
    AbstractIpAddressBasedQueue
    This abstract class manages two important aspects of an IpAddressBasedQueue.
    DomainUriTypePair
    Pair comprising a domain and a type.
    InMemoryQueue
    An IP-based queue which holds its data in memory.
    IpUriTypePair
    Pair of an IP and a URI type.
